    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all asylum seekers to live in remote areas of the UK & work with the EU",
        "additional_details": "We also urge the Government to work more closely with the EU as some asylum seekers may have obtained asylum in the EU or have status there.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to implement a policy which requires all asylum seekers to live in remote parts of the UK, such as offshore islands, away from cities and provide them with what they need there.",
